{"id": "1308701732368552016", "channel_id": "1308701732368552016", "type": 0, "author_id": "530336448474382347", "author_name": "latenpath", "author_bot": false, "content": "I use G-Ramona's Exalt (Ramona-Circuit) frequently, and every time I do, I have to scroll through a long list of Posses. But most of the time I want to quickly select the Posse I'm using.\n\nCurrently, the \"Confirm\" button cannot be pressed when no Posse is selected, and the \"X\" button will cancel the Exalt.\n\nI wish we could add QoL to her Exalt: automatically select the current Posse in use and allow to press \"Confirm\" immediately; or add a button right next to \"Confirm\" called \"Keep Current Posse\".\n\nThank you very much.", "timestamp": "2024-11-20T07:53:27.499000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1308701732871602196", "filename": "Morimens_12Y5JDLgbd.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1377893, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1308701732368552016/1308701732871602196/Morimens_12Y5JDLgbd.png?ex=69cc2637&is=69cad4b7&hm=4c140a16223ffca791c89790616f77529bef76f62910ae392a3ceab594c57882&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1308701732368552016", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Quick select current Posse when using G-Ramona Exalt", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
